&gt; 
&gt; 
&gt;             
&gt;           I was googling about AM radio reception, and I came across the below exchange on a forum. It talks about using the box to find missing persons (which I didn&#39;t know was possible), and the conversation mentions hearing specific voice inflections and recognizing a dead person&#39;s specific voice on the box. My question is, do any of you get a recognizable voice? The voices I get always sound robotic, although I do get clearly male or female voices. 
